vallibrary.measures
Class Clest

java.lang.Object
  vallibrary.measures.Measure
      vallibrary.measures.Clest

public class Clest
extends Measure

The Clest class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing CLEST measure. This class takes in input a Data_Matrix and an Input_Measure object. Values of measure are returned in a Measure_Vector object. The effect of computing such measure is basically to find a correct number of clusters with the given algorithm A and benchmark dataset D.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Raffaele Giancarlo, Filippo Utro, Davide Scaturro
